GCODING.item: PERFORM INIT_DATA_FORM IN PROGRAM ZSDSCMD0010 IF FOUND TABLES
READ TABLE GT_HEADER INDEX 1 INTO GS_HEADER.

FCODING.item: FORM CONVERT_DATE USING PV_DATE CHANGING PV_FULLDATE.
SPLIT PV_DATE AT '.' INTO lv_day lv_month lv_year.
CONCATENATE lv_day ' ' lv_month_name ' ' lv_year INTO PV_FULLDATE SEPARATED BY space.
